action.description: Passed Third Reading with Representative(s) Amato, Belatti, Grandinetti, Kapela, Perruso, Souza voting aye with reservations; Representative(s) Alcos, Garcia, Iwamoto, Matsumoto, Muraoka, Reyes Oda, Shimizu voting no (7) and Representative(s) Cochran, Pierick, Templo, Ward excused (4).
